snippet.title: Amber Heard Files For Divorce From Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
A sad story coming in today as the 15 month long marriage of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard comes to an end. With no prenup, this could get even more painful for all involved in the coming weeks.
